[Student "S"]
{NORTH has just 11 points, not enough to open the bidding. 
But when SOUTH opens 1\S NORTH should show her "almost opening strength" 
by jumping to 3\S.

SOUTH has just 13 points, and knowing NORTH has less than 13 he passes.}

